        Clause 5 [<span class="italic">Regulations under Part 1.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0610P0-05580'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0610P0_20000314_GCR_79' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Sainsbury of Turville</span> moved Amendment No. 15:
        <q>Page 5, line 29, after ("instrument") insert (", which (except in the case of the initial regulations) shall be").</q>
