        <span class="member">Lord Sainsbury of Turville</span> moved Amendment No. 26:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0610P0-05656'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0610P0_20000314_GCR_155' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
